# Begin Wireframes & Software Requirements

## User Stories

1.As a user of movie finder, I want to see the showtimes at the local theaters near me, so  I can pick a movie to go watch.
2.As a user,  I want to save the movies I am interested in watching.
3. As a user, I want to be able to add reviews on movies I got to watch.
4.As a user, I want to be able to delete movies that Iâ€™m no longer interested in watching.
5.As a user, I want to see movies near me by genre(stretch goal).
